    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-12-07T20:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-12-07T20:00:00-05:00" n="894"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d894">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">840.4016/12–745: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Czechoslovakia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Steinhardt</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-12-07T20:00:00-05:00"
                            >December 7, 1945—8 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>453. Please report reDeptel 316 Oct 19 whether you have been able to obtain any
                    unbiased first hand information on reports of persecution and expulsion of
                    Hungarian minority. Dept desires such info as may be available for use in
                    connection with (1) possible exchanges of views with Brit and Soviet Govts, (2)
                    consideration request of Hungarian FonMin (see Budapest’s 997 Nov 30 rptd you as
                    29), and (3) possible efforts on part of US Reps in Prague and Budapest to
                    impress on Czech (reDeptel 433 Dec 3 rpted Budapest as 769) and Hungarian Govts
                    desirability of direct compromise settlement.</p>
                <p>Sent Praha rptd Budapest.<note n="54" xml:id="d894fn1">As telegram 798.</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Byrnes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
